        analysisEn: 'A classic "growth insight" semi-open essay. The prompt suggests six directions (resilience/survival/patience/understanding/forgiveness/caring). Key: (1) choose a real-life event rather than empty moralizing; (2) show the transformation from "not knowing" to "learning"; (3) elevate to life insight at the end.',
